data.description: Nestled atop a hill sits 400 Hickory Way, in Northern Local SD & highly sought-after Thornhill Estates subdivision. This 1.41-acre property provides picturesque views & stunning sunsets. The home boasts 5 generously sized bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, large kitchen w/lots of cabinet & counter space, office w/built in's and so much more.  The fully finished lower level is perfect for hosting & entertaining, w/a custom-built bar. To top things off take a dip in the in-ground pool or unwind in the hot tub all while enjoying the beautiful scenery. Conveniently located this home is close to Buckeye Lake and all it has to offer & within minutes to I-70. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own in Thornville.  Updates list provided upon request.
